p-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-1-e1742031920740-150x150.webp 150w, https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-1-e1742031920740-350x350.webp 350w, https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-1-e1742031920740.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-10823\" src=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-3-768x1024.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\" srcset=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-3-768x1024.webp 768w, https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-3-225x300.webp 225w, https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-3.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-10824\" src=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-4-914x1024.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"914\" height=\"1024\" srcset=\"https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-4-914x1024.webp 914w, https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-4-268x300.webp 268w, https://ptemagic.com.vn/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/PTE-MAGI-Expert-Education-4.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 914px) 100vw, 914px\" /></p>\n<p>PTE Magic hẹn gặp lại các bạn ở những sự kiện tiếp theo của chúng tôi và các đối tác trong thời gian sắp tới.</p>\n", "featured_media": 10812, "segments": ["pte-magic-expert-education-tai-hoi-thao-du-hoc-toan-cau-2025"]}